\fs22
\b NexFlow Data Dictionary\b0\par
\par
\b Project:\b0 NexFlow\par
\b Database:\b0 PostgreSQL (via Prisma)\par
\b Prepared On:\b0 29 March 2026\par
\par
\b 1. User\b0\par
\b Purpose:\b0 Stores user profile and authentication identity.\par
\par
id | String | Not Null | PK | - | Unique user identifier\par
name | String | Not Null | - | - | User full/display name\par
email | String | Not Null | Unique | - | User email address\par
emailVerified | Boolean | Not Null | - | false | Email verification status\par
image | String | Nullable | - | null | Profile image URL\par
createdAt | DateTime | Not Null | - | now() | Record creation time\par
updatedAt | DateTime | Not Null | - | updatedAt | Last update time\par
\par
Relationships:\par
- One User has many Sessions\par
- One User has many Accounts\par
- One User has many Workflows\par
\par
\b 2. Session\b0\par
\b Purpose:\b0 Stores active login sessions and tokens.\par
\par
id | String | Not Null | PK | - | Session ID\par
expiresAt | DateTime | Not Null | - | - | Session expiry\par
token | String | Not Null | Unique | - | Session token\par
createdAt | DateTime | Not Null | - | now() | Created time\par
updatedAt | DateTime | Not Null | - | updatedAt | Updated time\par
ipAddress | String | Nullable | - | null | Client IP\par
userAgent | String | Nullable | - | null | Browser/device info\par
userId | String | Not Null | FK -> User.id, indexed | - | Session owner\par
\par
\b 3. Account\b0\par
\b Purpose:\b0 Stores linked authentication provider accounts.\par
\par
id | String | Not Null | PK | - | Account record ID\par
accountId | String | Not Null | - | - | Provider-side account ID\par
providerId | String | Not Null | - | - | Auth provider name/id\par
userId | String | Not Null | FK -> User.id, indexed | - | Owning user\par
accessToken | String | Nullable | - | null | OAuth access token\par
refreshToken | String | Nullable | - | null | OAuth refresh token\par
idToken | String | Nullable | - | null | OIDC ID token\par
accessTokenExpiresAt | DateTime | Nullable | - | null | Access token expiry\par
refreshTokenExpiresAt | DateTime | Nullable | - | null | Refresh token expiry\par
scope | String | Nullable | - | null | OAuth scopes\par
password | String | Nullable | - | null | Password hash (if local auth)\par
createdAt | DateTime | Not Null | - | now() | Created time\par
updatedAt | DateTime | Not Null | - | updatedAt | Updated time\par
\par
\b 4. Verification\b0\par
\b Purpose:\b0 Stores verification and recovery tokens.\par
\par
id | String | Not Null | PK | - | Verification record ID\par
identifier | String | Not Null | Indexed | - | Target identity (email, etc.)\par
value | String | Not Null | - | - | Verification token/code\par
expiresAt | DateTime | Not Null | - | - | Expiry time\par
createdAt | DateTime | Not Null | - | now() | Created time\par
updatedAt | DateTime | Not Null | - | updatedAt | Updated time\par
\par
\b 5. Workflow\b0\par
\b Purpose:\b0 Stores workflow metadata owned by a user.\par
\par
id | String | Not Null | PK | cuid() | Workflow ID\par
name | String | Not Null | - | - | Workflow name\par
createdAt | DateTime | Not Null | - | now() | Created time\par
updatedAt | DateTime | Not Null | - | updatedAt | Updated time\par
userId | String | Not Null | FK -> User.id | - | Owner user\par
\par
Relationships:\par
- One Workflow has many Nodes\par
- One Workflow has many Connections\par
\par
\b 6. Node\b0\par
\b Purpose:\b0 Stores workflow nodes (trigger/action/AI).\par
\par
id | String | Not Null | PK | cuid() | Node ID\par
workflowId | String | Not Null | FK -> Workflow.id | - | Parent workflow\par
name | String | Not Null | - | - | Node label\par
type | NodeType | Not Null | Enum | - | Node type\par
position | Json | Not Null | - | - | Canvas coordinates\par
data | Json | Not Null | - | {} | Node config/payload\par
createdAt | DateTime | Not Null | - | now() | Created time\par
updatedAt | DateTime | Not Null | - | updatedAt | Updated time\par
\par
Relationships:\par
- One Node can be source of many Connections\par
- One Node can be target of many Connections\par
\par
\b 7. Connection\b0\par
\b Purpose:\b0 Stores directed edges between nodes.\par
\par
id | String | Not Null | PK | cuid() | Connection ID\par
workflowId | String | Not Null | FK -> Workflow.id | - | Parent workflow\par
fromNodeId | String | Not Null | FK -> Node.id | - | Source node\par
toNodeId | String | Not Null | FK -> Node.id | - | Target node\par
fromOutput | String | Not Null | Composite unique part | main | Source handle\par
toInput | String | Not Null | Composite unique part | main | Target handle\par
createdAt | DateTime | Not Null | - | now() | Created time\par
updatedAt | DateTime | Not Null | - | updatedAt | Updated time\par
\par
Composite unique constraint:\par
(fromNodeId, toNodeId, fromOutput, toInput)\par
\par
\b 8. Enum Dictionary: NodeType\b0\par
\par
INITIAL | Initial/default workflow node\par
MANUAL_TRIGGER | User-triggered execution node\par
HTTP_REQUEST | HTTP call action node\par
GOOGLE_FORM_TRIGGER | Trigger from Google Form webhook\par
GMAIL_TRIGGER | Trigger from Gmail webhook\par
ANTHROPIC | Anthropic AI generation node\par
GEMINI | Google Gemini AI generation node\par
OPENAI | OpenAI AI generation node\par
\par
}
